#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs0.5"
msgid "8. Bhūtārocanasikkhāpada"
msgstr "The training rule on telling truthfully"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.24"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-pc.8.1"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.8.1.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.208"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa220"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying at Vesālī in the hall with the peaked "
"roof in the Great Wood."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā sandiṭṭhā sambhattā bhikkhū vaggumudāya "
"nadiyā tīre vassaṃ upagacchiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"At that time a number of monks who were friends had entered the rains on the "
"banks of the river Vaggumudā."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena vajjī dubbhikkhā hoti—dvīhitikā setaṭṭhikā "
"salākāvuttā, na sukarā uñchena paggahena yāpetuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Just then Vajjī was short of food and afflicted with hunger, with crops "
"blighted and turned to straw, and it was not easy to get by on almsfood."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ etadahosi—“etarahi kho vajjī dubbhikkhā—dvīhitikā "
"setaṭṭhikā salākāvuttā, na sukarā uñchena paggahena yāpetuṃ."
msgstr "The monks considered the difficult circumstances, and they thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.5"
msgid ""
"Kena nu kho mayaṃ upāyena samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ "
"vaseyyāma, na ca piṇḍakena kilameyyāmā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“How can we remain united and in harmony, have a comfortable rains, and get "
"almsfood without problems?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.6"
msgid "Ekacce evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "Some said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.7"
msgid "“handa mayaṃ, āvuso, gihīnaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhema."
msgstr "“We could do work for the lay people,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ te amhākaṃ dātuṃ maññissanti."
msgstr "and they’ll give something in return."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ mayaṃ samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasissāma, na ca "
"piṇḍakena kilamissāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In this way we’ll be united and in harmony, and we’ll spend the rains in "
"comfort and have no problems getting almsfood.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.10"
msgid "Ekacce evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "Some said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.11"
msgid "“alaṃ, āvuso, kiṃ gihīnaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhitena?"
msgstr "“There’s no need to do work for the lay people."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.12"
msgid "Handa mayaṃ, āvuso, gihīnaṃ dūteyyaṃ harāma."
msgstr "Let’s instead take messages for them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.13"
msgid "Evaṃ te amhākaṃ dātuṃ maññissanti."
msgstr "and they’ll give something in return."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.14"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ mayaṃ samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasissāma, na ca "
"piṇḍakena kilamissāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In this way we’ll be united and in harmony, and we’ll spend the rains in "
"comfort and have no problems getting almsfood.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.15"
msgid "Ekacce evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "Some said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.16"
msgid "“alaṃ, āvuso; kiṃ gihīnaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhitena."
msgstr "“There’s no need to do work for the lay people,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.17"
msgid "Kiṃ gihīnaṃ dūteyyaṃ haṭena."
msgstr "nor to take messages for them."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.209"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.18"
msgid ""
"Handa mayaṃ, āvuso, gihīnaṃ aññamaññassa uttarimanussadhammassa vaṇṇaṃ "
"bhāsissāma—"
msgstr ""
"Let’s instead praise one another’s superhuman qualities to the lay people, "

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.19"
msgid ""
"‘asuko bhikkhu paṭhamassa jhānassa lābhī, asuko bhikkhu dutiyassa jhānassa "
"lābhī, asuko bhikkhu tatiyassa jhānassa lābhī, asuko bhikkhu catutthassa "
"jhānassa lābhī, asuko bhikkhu sotāpanno, asuko bhikkhu sakadāgāmī, asuko "
"bhikkhu anāgāmī, asuko bhikkhu arahā, asuko bhikkhu tevijjo, asuko bhikkhu "
"chaḷabhiñño’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Such a monk has the first absorption, such a monk the second absorption, "
"such a monk the third, such a monk the fourth; such a monk is a stream-"
"enterer, such a monk a once-returner, such a non-returner, such a perfected "
"one; such a monk has the three true insights, and such the six direct "
"knowledges.’"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.20"
msgid "Evaṃ te amhākaṃ dātuṃ maññissanti."
msgstr "Then they’ll give to us."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.21"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ mayaṃ samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasissāma, na ca "
"piṇḍakena kilamissāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In this way we’ll be united and in harmony, and we’ll spend the rains in "
"comfort and have no problems getting almsfood."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.22"
msgid ""
"“Eso yeva kho, āvuso, seyyo, yo amhākaṃ gihīnaṃ aññamaññassa "
"uttarimanussadhammassa vaṇṇo bhāsito”ti."
msgstr ""
"Indeed, this is the better way, that we praise one another’s superhuman "
"qualities to the lay people.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa221"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.23"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū gihīnaṃ aññamaññassa uttarimanussadhammassa vaṇṇaṃ "
"bhāsiṃsu—"
msgstr "Then they praised each other’s superhuman qualities to the lay people,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.24"
msgid ""
"“asuko bhikkhu paṭhamassa jhānassa lābhī … pe … asuko bhikkhu chaḷabhiñño”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Such a monk has the first absorption … such a monk has the six direct "
"knowledges.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.25"
msgid "Atha kho te manussā—"
msgstr "And those people thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.26"
msgid ""
"“lābhā vata no, suladdhaṃ vata no, yesaṃ no evarūpā bhikkhū vassaṃ upagatā, "
"na vata no ito pubbe evarūpā bhikkhū vassaṃ upagatā, yathayime bhikkhū "
"sīlavanto kalyāṇadhammā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“We’re fortunate that such monks have come to us for the rains. Such monks "
"as these, who are virtuous and of good character, have never before entered "
"the rains with us.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.27"
msgid ""
"Te na tādisāni bhojanāni attanā bhuñjanti, mātāpitūnaṃ denti puttadārassa "
"denti dāsakammakaraporisassa denti mittāmaccānaṃ denti ñātisālohitānaṃ denti "
"yādisāni bhikkhūnaṃ denti."
msgstr ""
"And they gave such food and drink to those monks that they did not even eat "
"and drink themselves, or give to their parents, to their wives and children, "
"to their slaves, servants, and workers, to their friends and companions, or "
"to their relatives. "

#. VAR: sāyanti pivanti → attanā pivanti (bj, s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.28"
msgid ""
"Na tādisāni khādanīyāni sāyanīyāni pānāni attanā khādanti sāyanti pivanti "
"mātāpitūnaṃ denti puttadārassa denti dāsakammakaraporisassa denti "
"mittāmaccānaṃ denti ñātisālohitānaṃ denti, yādisāni bhikkhūnaṃ denti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.1.29"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū vaṇṇavā ahesuṃ pīṇindriyā pasannamukhavaṇṇā "
"vippasannachavivaṇṇā."
msgstr ""
"In this way those monks became handsome, with rounded features, bright "
"faces, and clear skin."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.25"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.8.1.2"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa222"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.1"
msgid ""
"Āciṇṇaṃ kho panetaṃ vassaṃvuṭṭhānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya "
"upasaṅkamituṃ."
msgstr ""
"Now it was the custom for monks who had finished keeping the rains to go and "
"see the Master."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.210"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū vassaṃvuṭṭhā temāsaccayena senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā "
"pattacīvaramādāya yena vesālī tena pakkamiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"So when the rainy-season residence was completed and the three months had "
"elapsed, those monks put their dwellings in order, took their bowls and "
"robes, and departed for Vesālī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.3"
msgid ""
"Anupubbena yena vesālī mahāvanaṃ kūṭāgārasālā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"When they eventually arrived at Vesālī, they went to the hall with the "
"peaked roof in the Great Wood."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.4"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"There they approached the Master, bowed down to him, and sat down to one "
"side."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.5"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena disāsu vassaṃvuṭṭhā bhikkhū kisā honti lūkhā dubbaṇṇā "
"uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajātā dhamanisanthatagattā."
msgstr ""
"At that time the monks who had completed the rainy-season residence in that "
"region were thin, haggard and pale, their veins protruding all over their "
"limbs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.6"
msgid ""
"Vaggumudātīriyā pana bhikkhū vaṇṇavā honti pīṇindriyā pasannamukhavaṇṇā "
"vippasannachavivaṇṇā."
msgstr ""
"But the monks from the banks of the Vaggumudā were handsome, with rounded "
"features, bright faces, and clear skin."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.7"
msgid ""
"Āciṇṇaṃ kho panetaṃ buddhānaṃ bhagavantānaṃ āgantukehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ "
"paṭisammodituṃ."
msgstr "It is the custom for Buddhas to greet newly arrived monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.8"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā vaggumudātīriye bhikkhū etadavoca—"
msgstr "and so the Master said to them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.9"
msgid ""
"“kacci, bhikkhave, khamanīyaṃ, kacci yāpanīyaṃ, kacci samaggā sammodamānā "
"avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasittha, na ca piṇḍakena kilamitthā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“I hope you’re keeping well, monks, I hope you’re comfortable; I hope you "
"spent the rains at ease, in concord and harmony, without dispute, and that "
"you had no trouble getting almsfood?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.10"
msgid "“Khamanīyaṃ, bhagavā, yāpanīyaṃ, bhagavā."
msgstr "“We’re keeping well, Master, we’re comfortable;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.11"
msgid ""
"Samaggā ca mayaṃ, bhante, sammodamānā avivadamānā phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasimhā, "
"na ca piṇḍakena kilamimhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"we spent the rains at ease, in concord and harmony, without dispute, and we "
"had no trouble getting almsfood.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.12"
msgid "Jānantāpi tathāgatā pucchanti, jānantāpi na pucchanti."
msgstr "Buddhas sometimes ask knowing, and knowing sometimes do not ask;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.13"
msgid "Kālaṃ viditvā pucchanti, kālaṃ viditvā na pucchanti."
msgstr ""
"they ask knowing the right time to ask, and they ask knowing the right time "
"not to ask."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.14"
msgid "Atthasañhitaṃ tathāgatā pucchanti, no anatthasañhitaṃ."
msgstr "Buddhas ask when it is beneficial, not when it is unbeneficial;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.15"
msgid "Anatthasañhite setughāto tathāgatānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"in regard to what is unbeneficial, the Buddhas have destroyed the bridge."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.16"
msgid "Dvīhākārehi buddhā bhagavanto bhikkhū paṭipucchanti—"
msgstr "Buddhas question the monks for two reasons:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.17"
msgid "“dhammaṃ vā desessāma, sāvakānaṃ vā sikkhāpadaṃ paññapessāmā”ti."
msgstr "to give a teaching or to lay down a training rule."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa223"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.18"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā vaggumudātīriye bhikkhū etadavoca—"
msgstr "And the Master said to those monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.19"
msgid ""
"“yathā kathaṃ pana tumhe, bhikkhave, samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā "
"phāsukaṃ vassaṃ vasittha, na ca piṇḍakena kilamitthā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“In what way, monks, did you spend the rains at ease, without having any "
"trouble getting almsfood?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.20"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ."
msgstr "And they told the Master what had happened."

#. </p><p><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.211"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.21"
msgid "“Kacci pana vo, bhikkhave, bhūtan”ti?"
msgstr "“But had you really achieved those superhuman qualities?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.22"
msgid "“Bhūtaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.23"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.24"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tumhe, bhikkhave, udarassa kāraṇā gihīnaṃ aññamaññassa "
"uttarimanussadhammassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsissatha."
msgstr ""
"“Monks, how can you for the sake of your stomachs praise one another’s "
"superhuman qualities to lay people?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.25"
msgid "Netaṃ, bhikkhave, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.26"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.26a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa224"></a>
#. <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.27"
msgid ""
"“Yo pana bhikkhu anupasampannassa uttarimanussadhammaṃ āroceyya bhūtasmiṃ, "
"pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If a monk truthfully tells a person who is not fully ordained of a "
"superhuman quality, he commits an offense entailing confession.’”"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs1.2.28"
msgid "(<em>8</em>:<strong>57</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-pc.8.2"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.8.2.1"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa225"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.4"
msgid "… pe … ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr ""
"… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order "
"through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa226"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.5"
msgid "Anupasampanno nāma"
msgstr "A person who is not fully ordained:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.6"
msgid "bhikkhuñca bhikkhuniñca ṭhapetvā, avaseso anupasampanno nāma."
msgstr "anyone except a fully ordained monk and a fully ordained nun."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa227"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.7"
msgid "Uttarimanussadhammo nāma"
msgstr "A superhuman quality:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.8"
msgid ""
"jhānaṃ, vimokkho, samādhi, samāpatti, ñāṇadassanaṃ, maggabhāvanā, "
"phalasacchikiriyā, kilesappahānaṃ, vinīvaraṇatā cittassa, suññāgāre abhirati."
msgstr ""
"absorption, release, stillness, attainment, knowledge and vision, "
"development of the path, realization of the fruits, abandoning the "
"defilements, a mind without hindrances, delighting in solitude."

#. </span>
#. </p><h2>
