#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa228"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.9"
msgid "Jhānanti"
msgstr "Absorption:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.10"
msgid "paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ, dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ, tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ, catutthaṃ jhānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"the first absorption, the second absorption, the third absorption, the "
"fourth absorption."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa229"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.11"
msgid "Vimokkhoti"
msgstr "Release:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.12"
msgid "suññato vimokkho, animitto vimokkho, appaṇihito vimokkho."
msgstr "emptiness release, signless release, desireless release."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.13"
msgid "Samādhīti"
msgstr "Stillness:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.14"
msgid "suññato samādhi, animitto samādhi, appaṇihito samādhi."
msgstr "emptiness stillness, signless stillness, desireless stillness."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.15"
msgid "Samāpattīti"
msgstr "Attainment:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.16"
msgid "suññatā samāpatti, animittā samāpatti, appaṇihitā samāpatti."
msgstr "emptiness attainment, signless attainment, desireless attainment."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.26"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa232"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.17"
msgid "Ñāṇadassananti"
msgstr "Knowledge and vision:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.18"
msgid "tisso vijjā."
msgstr "the three true insights."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa233"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.19"
msgid "Maggabhāvanāti"
msgstr "Development of the path:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"><a class="pts-vp-en" id="BD.2.212"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.20"
msgid ""
"cattāro satipaṭṭhānā, cattāro sammappadhānā, cattāro iddhipādā, "
"pañcindriyāni, pañca balāni, satta bojjhaṅgā, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo."
msgstr ""
"the four applications of mindfulness, the four right efforts, the four bases "
"of supernormal power, the five spiritual faculties, the five spiritual "
"powers, the seven factors of awakening, the noble eightfold path."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa234"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.21"
msgid "Phalasacchikiriyāti"
msgstr "Realization of the fruits:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
