msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.22"
msgid ""
"sotāpattiphalassa sacchikiriyā, sakadāgāmiphalassa sacchikiriyā, "
"anāgāmiphalassa sacchikiriyā, arahattassa sacchikiriyā."
msgstr ""
"realization of the fruit of stream-entry, realization of the fruit of once-"
"returning, realization of the fruit of non-returning, realization of "
"perfection."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa235"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.23"
msgid "Kilesappahānanti"
msgstr "Abandoning the defilements:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.24"
msgid "rāgassa pahānaṃ, dosassa pahānaṃ, mohassa pahānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"the abandoning of sensual desire, the abandoning of ill-will, the abandoning "
"of confusion."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa236"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.25"
msgid "Vinīvaraṇatā cittassāti"
msgstr "A mind without hindrances:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.26"
msgid ""
"rāgā cittaṃ vinīvaraṇatā, dosā cittaṃ vinīvaraṇatā, mohā cittaṃ vinīvaraṇatā."
msgstr ""
"a mind without sensual desire, a mind without ill-will, a mind without "
"confusion."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa237"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.27"
msgid "Suññāgāre abhiratīti"
msgstr "Delighting in solitude:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.1.28"
msgid ""
"paṭhamena jhānena suññāgāre abhirati, dutiyena jhānena suññāgāre abhirati, "
"tatiyena jhānena suññāgāre abhirati, catutthena jhānena suññāgāre abhirati."
msgstr ""
"because of the first absorption there is delight in solitude, because of the "
"second absorption there is delight in solitude, because of the third "
"absorption there is delight in solitude, because of the fourth absorption "
"there is delight in solitude."

