msgstr ""
"has realized the first absorption,” he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="66"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa285"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.6"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.7"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.8"
msgid "“yo te vihāre vasi so bhikkhu dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "“The monk who stayed in your dwelling attained the second absorption …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.9"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"the third absorption … the fourth absorption … is attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.10"
msgid "so bhikkhu catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.11"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the fourth absorption,” he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="67"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa286"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.12"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.13"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.14"
msgid "“yo te vihāre vasi so bhikkhu suññataṃ vimokkhaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "“The monk who stayed in your dwelling attained the emptiness release …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.15"
msgid ""
"animittaṃ vimokkhaṃ appaṇihitaṃ vimokkhaṃ suññataṃ samādhiṃ animittaṃ "
"samādhiṃ appaṇihitaṃ samādhiṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"the signless release … the desireless release … the emptiness stillness … "
"the signless stillness … the desireless stillness … is attaining … has "
"attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.16"
msgid "so bhikkhu appaṇihitassa samādhissa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.17"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā appaṇihito samādhi sacchikato”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the desireless stillness,” he commits an offense of wrong "
"conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="68"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa287"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.18"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.19"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.20"
msgid "“yo te vihāre vasi so bhikkhu suññataṃ samāpattiṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“The monk who stayed in your dwelling attained the emptiness attainment …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.21"
msgid ""
"animittaṃ samāpattiṃ appaṇihitaṃ samāpattiṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, "
"samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"the signless attainment … the desireless attainment … is attaining … has "
"attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.22"
msgid "appaṇihitāya samāpattiyā lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.23"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā appaṇihitā samāpatti sacchikatā”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the desireless attainment,” he commits an offense of wrong "
"conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="69"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.30"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa288"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.24"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.25"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.26"
msgid "“yo te vihāre vasi so bhikkhu tisso vijjā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“The monk who stayed in your dwelling attained the three true insights …"

#. VAR: arahattaṃ → arahattaphalaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.27"
msgid ""
"cattāro satipaṭṭhāne, cattāro sammappadhāne, cattāro iddhipāde, "
"pañcindriyāni, pañca balāni, satta bojjhaṅge, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ, "
"sotāpattiphalaṃ, sakadāgāmiphalaṃ, anāgāmiphalaṃ, arahattaṃ samāpajji … "
"samāpajjati, samāpanno … pe …"
msgstr ""
"the four applications of mindfulness … the four right efforts … the four "
"bases for supernormal power … the five spiritual faculties … the five "
"spiritual powers … the seven factors of awakening … the noble eightfold path "
"… the fruit of stream entry … the fruit of once-returning … the fruit of non-"
"returning … perfection … is attaining … has attained … obtains … masters … "
"has realized …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.28"
msgid ""
"tassa bhikkhuno rāgo catto, doso catto, moho catto, vanto, mutto, pahīno, "
"paṭinissaṭṭho, ukkheṭito, samukkheṭito;"
msgstr ""
"has given up sensual desire … has given up ill-will … has given up "
"confusion, renounced it, let it go, abandoned it, relinquished it, forsaken "
"it, thrown it aside …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.29"
msgid ""
"tassa bhikkhuno rāgā cittaṃ vinīvaraṇaṃ, dosā cittaṃ vinīvaraṇaṃ, mohā "
"cittaṃ vinīvaraṇan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has a mind free from the hindrance of sensual desire … has a mind free from "
"the hindrance of ill-will … has a mind free from the hindrance of confusion,”"
" he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="70"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa289"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.30"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.31"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.32"
msgid "“yo te vihāre vasi so bhikkhu suññāgāre paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“The monk who stayed in your dwelling attained the first absorption in an "
"empty dwelling …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.33"
msgid ""
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, "
"samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"the second absorption … the third absorption … the fourth absorption … is "
"attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.34"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.35"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="71"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa290"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.36"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.37"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.38"
msgid ""
"“yo te cīvaraṃ paribhuñji, yo te piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñji, yo te senāsanaṃ "
"paribhuñji, yo te gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ paribhuñji so bhikkhu "
"suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"“The monk who made use of your robe-cloth … who made use of your almsfood … "
"who made use of your dwelling … who made use of your medicines attained the "
"fourth absorption in an empty dwelling … is attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.39"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.40"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="72"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa291"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.41"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.42"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.43"
msgid ""
"“yena te vihāro paribhutto … pe … yena te cīvaraṃ paribhuttaṃ, yena te "
"piṇḍapāto paribhutto, yena te senāsanaṃ paribhuttaṃ, yena te "
"gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāro paribhutto so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthaṃ "
"jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"“The monk who has made use of your dwelling … who has made use of your robe-"
"cloth … who has made use of your almsfood … who has made use of your "
"dwelling … who has made use of your medicines attained the fourth absorption "
"in an empty dwelling … is attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.44"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.45"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="73"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa292"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.46"
msgid "Āroceyyāti"
msgstr "Tells:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.47"
msgid "anupasampannassa—"
msgstr "if a monk says to a person who is not fully ordained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.48"
msgid ""
"“yaṃ tvaṃ āgamma vihāraṃ adāsi … pe … cīvaraṃ adāsi, piṇḍapātaṃ adāsi, "
"senāsanaṃ adāsi, gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhāraṃ adāsi so bhikkhu "
"suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji, samāpajjati, samāpanno;"
msgstr ""
"“The monk to whom you gave a dwelling … to whom you gave robe-cloth … to "
"whom you gave almsfood … to whom you gave a dwelling … to whom you gave "
"medicines … he attained the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling … is "
"attaining … has attained …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.49"
msgid "so bhikkhu suññāgāre catutthassa jhānassa lābhī, vasī;"
msgstr "obtains … masters …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.5.50"
msgid ""
"tena bhikkhunā suññāgāre catutthaṃ jhānaṃ sacchikatan”ti bhaṇantassa āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"has realized the fourth absorption in an empty dwelling,” he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.6.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="74"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.8.2.6"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa293"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.6.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.6.2"
msgid "upasampannassa, bhūtaṃ āroceti,"
msgstr "if he truthfully tells one who is fully ordained;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.6.3"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="75"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa294"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc8:pts-cs2.6.4"
msgid "Bhūtārocanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr "The eighth rule, the training rule on telling truthfully, is finished."

